<item>
            <title>[LU-4172] Test failure on test suite recovery-small test_26b: Client was not evicted by ost rc=1</title>
                <link>https://jira.whamcloud.com/browse/LU-4172</link>
                <project id="10000" key="LU">Lustre</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;This issue was created by maloo for sarah &amp;lt;sarah@whamcloud.com&amp;gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;This issue relates to the following test suite run: &lt;a href=&quot;http://maloo.whamcloud.com/test_sets/553eecec-399c-11e3-8e4c-52540035b04c&quot; class=&quot;external-link&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot; rel=&quot;nofollow noopener&quot;&gt;http://maloo.whamcloud.com/test_sets/553eecec-399c-11e3-8e4c-52540035b04c&lt;/a&gt;.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;The sub-test test_26b failed with the following error:&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;blockquote&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Client was not evicted by ost rc=1&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/blockquote&gt;

&lt;p&gt;client console&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;div class=&quot;preformatted panel&quot; style=&quot;border-width: 1px;&quot;&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;preformattedContent panelContent&quot;&gt;
&lt;pre&gt;21:31:42:Lustre: DEBUG MARKER: == recovery-small test 26b: evict dead exports == 21:31:35 (1382243495)
21:31:42:Lustre: Evicted from MGS (at 10.10.4.186@tcp) after server handle changed from 0x1ea7a812e69b79f0 to 0x1ea7a812e69b7fd1
21:31:42:LustreError: 167-0: lustre-MDT0000-mdc-ffff880024158c00: This client was evicted by lustre-MDT0000; in progress operations using this service will fail.
21:31:42:LustreError: Skipped 1 previous similar message
21:31:42:LustreError: 16106:0:(lmv_obd.c:1509:lmv_statfs()) can&apos;t stat MDS #0 (lustre-MDT0000-mdc-ffff880024158c00), error -5
21:31:42:LustreError: 16106:0:(llite_lib.c:1606:ll_statfs_internal()) md_statfs fails: rc = -5
21:31:42:LustreError: 10107:0:(mdc_locks.c:915:mdc_enqueue()) ldlm_cli_enqueue: -5
21:31:42:LustreError: 10107:0:(vvp_io.c:1227:vvp_io_init()) lustre: refresh file layout [0x20000fe01:0x34:0x0] error -5.
21:31:42:Lustre: DEBUG MARKER: mkdir -p /mnt/lustre2
21:31:42:Lustre: DEBUG MARKER: mount -t lustre -o user_xattr,acl,flock client-30vm3:client-30vm7:/lustre /mnt/lustre2
21:31:42:LustreError: 152-6: Ignoring deprecated mount option &apos;acl&apos;.
21:31:43:Lustre: Layout lock feature supported.
21:31:43:Lustre: Mounted lustre-client
21:31:43:LNet: 16140:0:(debug.c:218:libcfs_debug_str2mask()) You are trying to use a numerical value for the mask - this will be deprecated in a future release.
21:31:45:Lustre: DEBUG MARKER: grep -c /mnt/lustre2&apos; &apos; /proc/mounts
21:31:45:Lustre: DEBUG MARKER: lsof -t /mnt/lustre2
21:31:45:Lustre: DEBUG MARKER: umount -f /mnt/lustre2 2&amp;gt;&amp;amp;1
21:31:45:Lustre: setting import lustre-MDT0000_UUID INACTIVE by administrator request
21:31:45:Lustre: setting import lustre-OST0000_UUID INACTIVE by administrator request
21:31:45:Lustre: Unmounted lustre-client
21:32:56:Lustre: DEBUG MARKER: /usr/sbin/lctl mark  recovery-small test_26b: @@@@@@ FAIL: Client was not evicted by ost rc=1 
&lt;/pre&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;</description>
